high_descs: Go across the kitchen to the table, and turn right to go to the right side of the table.
Pick up the knife on the back of the table, between the two cups.
Step back from the table.
Cut the potato in front of the coffee cup, on the table, into slices.
Step to the left of the table.
Place the knife on the table to the left of the sliced potato.
Move back over to the right of the table, in front of the potato.
Pick up one of the potato slices on the table.
Turn around towards the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice in the refrigerator, on the top shelf, to the left of the egg, wait a moment for the potato slice to chill, then remove the tomato slice from the refrigerator.
Step back from the refrigerator, and to the left so that you are in front of the garbage bin on the floor, to the left of the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice in the garbage bin, on the floor, to the left of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold potato slice in the garbage can.

high_descs: Turn and go to the round table.
Pick up a knife on the round table.
Turn and go to the round table.
Cut a potato on the round table.
Turn and go to the round table.
Put the knife on the round table.
Turn and go to the round table.
Pick up a slice of potato on the round table.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill a slice of potato in the refrigerator.
Turn and go to the trash can.
Put the slice of potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of potato in the trash can.
